high_descs: Go straight and head to the small black table
Grab the large knife off of the black table
Cut the cabbage on the table into slices
Turn around and face the white table on the left
Put the knife down on the table
Turn right and go to the small black table
Grab a slice of cabbage
Turn around and head to the oven
Put the cabbage in the pan on the right
Grab the pan on the right
Turn left and stop at the white table on the left
Put the pan on the table
anns.task_desc: Placing a large pan with sliced cabbage in it on a white table

high_descs: Walk to the small black table to the right of the black trash bag in the corner.
Pick up the yellow knife behind the salt on the table.
Cut up the lettuce on the table.
Turn left to face the white table.
Plate the knife on the white table.
Turn right to face the small black table.
Pick up piece of lettuce from the black table.
Turn around and walk to the stove.
Place the lettuce in the pot on the right of the stove.
Pick up the pot on the right of the stove.
Turn right and walk to the white table with the yellow knife on it.
Place the pot on the back right corner of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with lettuce in it on the white table to the left of the black trash bag.

high_descs: Walk to the white table in front of you then turn right and face the brown shelf
Pick up the knife from the brown shelf.
Slice the head of lettuce on the brown shelf with the knife.
Turn left and face the white table with the toaster on it.
Put the knife on the white table.
Turn right to face the brown shelf.
Take a lettuce slice from the brown shelf.
Turn around and walk to the stove on the right.
Put the lettuce slice in the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot on the stove with the lettuce in it.
Turn right and walk to the white table on the left.
Place the pot with the lettuce in it on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Cut a head of lettuce, place a slice in a pot, put the pot on the white table.
